<h5><code>generation_timeout</code></h5>
<span data-as="p">This error occurs when the requested operation took longer than the allowed time limit to complete.</span>
<ul>
<li><strong>Status Code:</strong> 504</li>
<li><strong>Retryable:</strong> Can be <code>true</code> or <code>false</code>.</li>
<li><strong>Context (<code>ctx</code>):</strong> None</li>
</ul>
