<h5><code>file_download_error</code></h5>
<span data-as="p">This error indicates that the server failed to download a file specified by a URL in the input.
Make sure the URL is publicly accessible and that the file is not behind a login or authentication wall.</span>
<ul>
<li><strong>Status Code:</strong> 422</li>
<li><strong>Retryable:</strong> <code>false</code>.</li>
