<h5><code>sequence_too_long</code></h5>
<span data-as="p">This error occurs when a sequence (like a list or string) has more items/characters than the allowed maximum length.</span>
<ul>
<li><strong>Status Code:</strong> 422</li>
<li><strong>Retryable:</strong> <code>false</code>.</li>
<li><strong>Context (<code>ctx</code>):</strong>
<ul>
<li><code>max_length</code>: The maximum allowed length of the sequence.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
