<h5><code>invalid_archive</code></h5>
<span data-as="p">This error occurs when the provided archive file (e.g., .zip, .tar) cannot be read or processed, likely due to corruption or an unsupported format.</span>
<ul>
<li><strong>Status Code:</strong> 422</li>
<li><strong>Retryable:</strong> <code>false</code>.</li>
<li><strong>Context (<code>ctx</code>):</strong>
<ul>
<li><code>supported_extensions</code>: A list of supported archive file extensions.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
