<h5><code>audio_duration_too_long</code></h5>
<span data-as="p">This error indicates that the provided audio file exceeds the maximum allowed duration.</span>
<ul>
<li><strong>Status Code:</strong> 422</li>
<li><strong>Retryable:</strong> <code>false</code>.</li>
<li><strong>Context (<code>ctx</code>):</strong>
<ul>
<li><code>max_duration</code>: The maximum allowed duration in seconds.</li>
<li><code>provided_duration</code>: The duration of the provided audio file in seconds.</li>
</ul>
</li>
